dct_title_s: Rutgers College of Agriculture and Environmental Science, New Jersey 1973
dct_description_sm: Map of the Rutgers University College of Agriculture and Environmental Science occupying the present day Douglass Campus. Includes building directory. Map includes portion of campus in New Brunswick borough and the outlying departments in North Brunswick Township including the Rutgers Gardens property and the horticulture farms.
